---
title: Salmon in Lemon Beurre Blanc Sauce with Chive Roasted Fingerling Potatoes & Avocado Orange Salad
description: Dazzle your dinner guests with this spring-inspired seared salmon dish, complete with a delicate French-style shallot sauce whisked with butter and crème fraîche. Roasted fingerling potatoes invite any runaway sauce and a sprinkle of chives reminds you that spring has sprung. On the side is a colorful arugula salad, bejeweled with fresh orange, avocado, and walnuts. Bright, balanced, and effortlessly elegant—this French favorite is dressed to impress!
